This is the protocol for a review and there is no abstract. The objectives are as follows:, Primary objective:, To compare in head-to-head trials the effect of specific first-line antihypertensive drugs on morbidity, mortality and drop-outs due to adverse drug effects in patients with hypertension., Secondary objective:, To compare the percentage of patients requiring dose titration, addition of a second or third drug, and switching to other therapy in the same trials., To compare the blood pressure lowering efficacy according to the specific first-line therapy in the same trials